<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>15: I saw 5 groups of 3, which is 15. I counted by 3 five times like 3, 6, 9, 12, 15.</li>
      <li>18: I know that 5 groups of 3 is 15 and one more group of 3 is 18.</li>
      <li>24: I saw 5 groups of 4 and 1 more group of 4. Five groups of 4 is 20 and one more group of 4 makes 24.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


